Class PSWepFixImages

java.lang.Object
  com.percussion.extension.PSDefaultExtension
      com.percussion.extensions.general.PSFileInfo
          com.percussion.ce.PSWepFixImages
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPSExtension, IPSRequestPreProcessor
public class PSWepFixImages
extends PSFileInfo
implements IPSRequestPreProcessor

This class is a Rhythmyx pre-exit which examines incoming Xml, gets HTML content from 'wepbodyhtml' parameter; Parses it, then looks for all the 'img' tags and for each of those first checks whether height and width attributes are already set; if those are not set then it grabs the actual image, calculates its dimentions and sets width, height, rxwidth and rxheight on the img tag.
